{
  "stem": "428.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I go out one Sunday, and I met the rabbi from my town.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "He used to go-- he-- he wasn't living as a-- as a Jew.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "He was living as a-- as a priest, something like this.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But he lived through the war.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And I met the rabbi from my little town.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I have them on the picture over here.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I met the rabbi.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And then I used-- we went out and we met that German, the German who was in the army, officer, whatever he was-- that he took-- he took me to work in the garage.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "He took my friend to work in the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And then-- and then I went to-- then I went there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I don't know for how long, a month or two, I was working by them in the garage, sleeping with the army, everything to eat in there.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I used to-- I used to work in the garage, for instance.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "This was in Germany-- Starnberg by-- by Munich, Starnberg, in Germany.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "No, no, this was in Ebensee, in Austria.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "But after being with them-- with the army two or three weeks, they transferred out our columns to Bayern, Germany.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And they took me with them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And I was in Germany.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "There was Starnberg on Bordensee.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "This was beautiful, by the sea.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And I was with them working in the garage.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "For instance, if-- I used to-- I used to drive us to the [?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "Becker. ?] I used to go to pick up gasoline.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "They have certain places where they have gasoline in that tanks.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "I used to pick up this and bring this there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "When our-- when our-- when our-- when our Jeep got a flat, I used to go and fix the flat for them.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "Yeah, I was working there.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
